Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier而那也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.13,0:00:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.30,0:00:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同时站在火线的两端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.94,0:00:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绕过危险的转角 追过生与死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.48,0:00:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑战谎言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.29,0:00:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论编织出多少谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.96,0:00:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相还是会照出光明的轮廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.17,0:00:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.70,0:00:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.27,0:00:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当我们的痛苦都抛在脑后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.51,0:00:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.14,0:00:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.81,0:01:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是士兵不是站着就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.25,0:01:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.75,0:01:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,占好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.32,0:01:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它们留给审判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.69,0:01:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.26,0:01:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.86,0:01:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牺牲的时候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.73,0:01:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只能奋起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.33,0:01:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻壳机动队 S．A．C．2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.18,0:02:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果我们还是跟事实无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.45,0:02:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直在找赎罪的机会也是事实啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.16,0:02:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对亚裔各国来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.76,0:02:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受过上个世纪战后教育的人也许更是如此呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.33,0:02:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一面对亚裔和欧洲的战争袖手旁观
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.44,0:02:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一面却在各地打第二次越南战争也是相同的道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.74,0:02:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有这个救济基金的数字也是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.98,0:02:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经不能再喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.91,0:02:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把这个也当成税金不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.52,0:02:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是说不过会长呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.55,0:03:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住...住手 基诺...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饶...饶了我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.55,0:03:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求...求求你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.29,0:03:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基诺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.79,0:03:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基诺?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.80,0:03:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基诺，你怎么了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.17,0:03:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晃动稍微大了一点哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.77,0:03:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常抱歉 会长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.85,0:03:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#02饱食终日的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.99,0:03:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.92,0:03:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要去那家店吃牡蛎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.12,0:03:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可是极品哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我有点事 今天就不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.69,0:04:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么啊 又是你那个正职吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.43,0:04:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是努力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是可悲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.74,0:04:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用人工内脏的义体人根本不需要食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.17,0:04:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更何况对全部感觉器官都数字化的他来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.41,0:04:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,享受美食的这种行为不过只是一种怀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.26,0:04:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.36,0:04:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又被公安盯上了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.53,0:04:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是说中松的事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.07,0:04:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说又被甩了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.77,0:04:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,义体人专用食品...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.57,0:04:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仔细想想他们其实也是受害者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.18,0:04:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被徽召去打通称为第二次越南载争的第四次非核大载
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.11,0:04:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依照从军的规定动手术换上高性能电子脑和部分义体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.49,0:05:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家常锐“载争就是跨国企业的商品展示会“
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.59,0:05:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使电子脑化、义体化技术获得飞跃进步的实验场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是上次大战的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.70,0:05:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们没有发现自己曾是白老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在失去自己的身体、家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至是国土的同时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.57,0:05:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紧紧抓住微薄的给付以及分配到的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.07,0:05:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乍看之下好象正在享受幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.38,0:05:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就不知道这是从电子脑和义体构成的虚拟人格中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.61,0:05:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,产生出来的虚假快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.95,0:05:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,针对招慰难民居住区的连续爆炸案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警视厅联合搜查本部刚刚宣布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.79,0:05:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾收到个别主义者的恐怖组织所发出的犯罪声明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.03,0:05:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根据声明来看该组织要求亚裔难民离开日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.67,0:05:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并且把他们一连串的犯罪行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.93,0:05:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,界定为对亚裔难民主导的暴动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.84,0:05:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和难民救济措施导致的财政缺口所做的报复行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.11,0:06:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媒盟只会照单全收当局发表的内容然后报导出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.21,0:06:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明知是谎言 却还是操纵情报获取利益
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.15,0:06:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是他们的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.76,0:06:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媒体希望得到什么 想要去尝试些什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.96,0:06:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要窥视一下他们的夜生活就可以知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.57,0:06:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们连客观判断自己所为是否 已然沉溺于享乐的能力都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.94,0:06:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是不断嘲笑愚昧的一般民众
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.69,0:06:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要看三大网络的会长片仓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.96,0:06:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何评论在高级日式餐厅天天聚餐的人 一切就很清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.83,0:06:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合执政党党代表阶级的不必说一定有份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.03,0:06:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有掌握各省厅高级官僚身上电子脑和义体专利权的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.04,0:06:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那群跨国企业干部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.47,0:07:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,片仓根本没有报导真相的气概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.74,0:07:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有的只是维持自己帝国的欲望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.22,0:07:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(新滨市上空)(失火的政府大楼)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.62,0:07:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(政府大楼遭到攻击)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.59,0:07:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现场仍然冒着浓烟(于政府大楼前线报导)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.79,0:07:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仿佛诉说着反对难民政策的亚裔难民所主导的官署攻击行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,规模相当大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.17,0:07:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下手不够重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.80,0:07:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样根本无法了结任何事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.84,0:07:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也无法让任何事情开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.71,0:07:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Reset The world
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媒体才是真正的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.38,0:07:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些家伙跟执政当局连手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.55,0:07:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大声地假装自己是正义的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.92,0:07:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是他们不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里有个知道一切的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.19,0:07:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有个知道真相并决心达成理想的坚强意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.03,0:08:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必须尽快执行他的死刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是上天赋予知道真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.97,0:08:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且为了探求真相无谓死亡之人的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.32,0:08:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上个世纪初 一位伟大的犹太作家曾这样说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.96,0:08:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能存在没有真实的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.53,0:08:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所谓真实恐怕就是人生本身吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.93,0:08:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且这里才存在着真实的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.95,0:08:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的美丽毫无疑问就是真实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.32,0:08:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种身为一个生命体的毫无修饰的美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.03,0:09:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有把快乐当成快乐来享受的一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.23,0:09:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有为了生存而切割出来 没有参杂任何多余事物的纯洁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.03,0:09:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一看就知道她全身都是义体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.54,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她完美的肉体无法跟特化用来享乐的目的切割开来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这才是美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.31,0:09:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我确信只有她才是真正的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.19,0:09:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她身上可以看到某种为了维护身为人的尊严而顽强保护的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.44,0:09:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在她的精神面前任何东西都黯淡无光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.14,0:09:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算发挥金钱的力量把她得到手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.51,0:09:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不可能得到她的意志、美丽以及真实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.13,0:10:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.24,0:10:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论什么人都不可能占有真实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.01,0:10:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使他们使用权利威吓我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.28,0:10:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并且想要玩弄我们的心灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一个人知道真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.81,0:11:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而那个人除了我之外别无他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.62,0:11:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.99,0:11:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天世界将在真实中醒来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.13,0:11:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天终于到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.70,0:11:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要请假就说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道你那是正职还是兼职
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.81,0:11:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安排片仓会长专属驾驶员这种高级工作给你可是你的荣幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.18,0:11:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的技术的确是最棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是大战时的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.89,0:11:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 我告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.39,0:11:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你们这种伤残战斗义体人原本就没有什么工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.70,0:11:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.40,0:11:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前你不是这种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.20,0:12:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时候的你至少拥有面对真实的勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.27,0:12:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是以前的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.04,0:12:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该不会放任片仓那样的人为所欲为才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.55,0:12:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时...时代不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了活下去不得不这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.85,0:12:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已经忘记我为什么离开军队跟随你到现在了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.03,0:12:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你有没有在听啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你刚刚在嘀咕什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.34,0:12:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.54,0:12:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那边的事就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看对方的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.12,0:12:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.82,0:12:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.92,0:12:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咋天很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.92,0:12:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擅自请假没来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.59,0:12:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.93,0:12:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有这回事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.67,0:12:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.87,0:13:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 没事 另外...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.47,0:13:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶 可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.05,0:13:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明需要我的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.22,0:13:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却故意装成一副不记得的模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.42,0:13:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个有虐待狂的混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.16,0:13:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我稍微谦虚一下他就得寸进尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.83,0:13:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你们这种人只要我动一下操纵杆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.38,0:13:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的心中没有一丝犹豫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.85,0:13:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我并不吝于为可怜的大众奉献生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.15,0:13:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 就算我将片仓从这个世界除去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.63,0:14:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还是害怕这件事情会被那些家伙的网络掩盖起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.13,0:14:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果变成那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.77,0:14:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相就不会传达到世界上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.97,0:14:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了不发生这种事有必要把真相先告诉某个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老婆变得不听我的话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.88,0:14:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那真是糟糕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.35,0:14:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你得好好服务一下哄她高兴才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.86,0:14:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.82,0:14:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶尔陪我喝一杯怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.46,0:14:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不然去你之前说过吃得到牡蛎的那家店也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.40,0:14:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真难得呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.66,0:14:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生什么事了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也没什么啦 老实说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.30,0:14:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看样子我最近就不得不为了那个正职辞掉这份工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.34,0:14:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.04,0:14:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 你升官啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.21,0:14:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是令人羡慕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.71,0:14:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 也不是那样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.31,0:14:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是这个原因的话 我实在很想陪你去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是今天实在没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.75,0:15:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就算了 没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.07,0:15:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了虚无飘渺的目的 以及维护一部分人的权力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.04,0:15:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被迫奔向战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.44,0:15:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁都无法理解我在那里失去的东西有多巨大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.83,0:15:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想用这些钱买下她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.54,0:15:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.67,0:15:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么一点根本不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.54,0:15:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.28,0:16:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在战争当中失去重要事物的不只有你一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.33,0:16:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 到此为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.46,0:16:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不是什么都还没做吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.17,0:16:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下去的要另外收钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.14,0:16:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我付订金的时候不是连入会金都交了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.74,0:16:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.90,0:16:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饶了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.03,0:16:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是那些钱被拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.33,0:16:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的老婆孩子就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.50,0:16:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没...没有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.21,0:17:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饭吃了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.80,0:17:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您好 这里是招慰难民救济基金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.44,0:17:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是响应你们幕款的人(目前在日本有失去祖国的)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.58,0:17:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢您平日的照顾(300万难民)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.91,0:17:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个...因为出了点事情(现在正是展现互助精神的时候)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.28,0:17:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可不可以中止对你们的转帐汇款?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.22,0:17:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.55,0:17:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉无法识别你的申请事项
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.43,0:17:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想中止对你们的汇款
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.86,0:17:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想取消登记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.26,0:18:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我为您从头介绍申请手续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.37,0:18:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要询问申请基金的事项请按1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.91,0:18:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其它的询问事项请按2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.94,0:18:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久违的一场压倒性胜利呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.71,0:18:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 你说那场选代表的比赛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.78,0:18:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那记右钩拳真是厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我感动死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么会想吃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.59,0:18:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是不需要吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么会想吃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.33,0:18:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是不需要吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.50,0:18:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?为什么?为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.04,0:18:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么会想吃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.57,0:18:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是本能 这不是真实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.31,0:18:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是吓了我一大跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.61,0:18:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到那家伙会被公安抓走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.15,0:18:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是不是早就知道那家伙是亚裔的人了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.49,0:18:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.66,0:18:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基诺啊 他们不是很熟吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.13,0:19:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他怎么可能会知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.80,0:19:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.00,0:19:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.07,0:19:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚裔难民主导的官署攻击事件已经抓到实施犯罪的嫌犯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.04,0:19:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三泽阳一 又名杨岷台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.38,0:19:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在被警官铐住双手带出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.05,0:19:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是确信将会胜利的手势吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.19,0:19:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么...会是他?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.49,0:19:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逮捕这次实施犯罪的嫌犯后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.46,0:19:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经有三个"亚裔难民支持团体"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.23,0:19:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及"招慰难民人权及保障协会"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.23,0:19:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,召开了前所未见的记者会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.30,0:19:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们发表声明表示他的行为是替每天遭受到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.27,0:19:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无理歧视的亚洲、日本双方难民发出抗议的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.57,0:19:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一连串的犯罪行为按其情节 尚有斟酌的余地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.34,0:19:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故 意求减轻刑责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.49,0:20:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你送一下这位客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.85,0:20:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.32,0:20:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,片仓对你做了什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.72,0:20:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.03,0:20:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在找你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.70,0:20:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这几天一直都...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.37,0:20:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 应该说从还没出生以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.77,0:20:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.81,0:20:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会再让你遇到痛苦的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.88,0:20:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就这样两个人一起到远方去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.01,0:21:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到一个谁都无法打扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.05,0:21:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只属于我们的国度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.25,0:21:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 在那之前我有件事情无论如何一定要去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想做什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.79,0:21:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我必须...解放真实才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.16,0:21:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带着我一起吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.61,0:21:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已经拼命战斗过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你胜利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.72,0:21:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是那样就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.30,0:21:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚接到石川的联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.11,0:22:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙似乎跟这一连串的恐怖活动无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.91,0:22:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根据他在军中的经历他失去下半身跟作战行动无关
